      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant work to be roadworthy again. The engine struggles to start and idles roughly, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Externally, the body shows several large dents, significant paint fading, and areas of surface rust. The interior has seen better days, with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This is a project car sold strictly as-is, ideal for someone looking for parts or a complete restoration challenge.",
