      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exemplary specimen maintained to the most exacting automotive standards. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of fastidious care. Every component has been rigorously scrutinized to ensure it meets our benchmarks for both mechanical precision and aesthetic excellence. This represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of unrivaled caliber, suited for the most discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
